RawLine: ITEM_700057_Tip,將令牌給守衛看，可前往第三域。令牌正面有玄武紋樣，並附有『密穴土道，草甲覆之，刀槍不入，冷熱不侵。』這段文字。,将令牌给守卫看，可前往第三域。令牌正面有玄武纹样，并附有『密穴土道，草甲覆之，刀枪不入，冷热不侵。』这段文字。

Items.mt: Show the token to the guard and you can go to the third domain. On the front of the token is the Xuanwu pattern, with the text: "A secret cave and earth path, covered with grass armor, invulnerable to swords and spears, hot and cold. This text.
